<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10413996>
    dc:description "Figure2.Samadinia pulchra(Miers in Tizard,Moseley, Buchanan& Murray,1885),holotype male (pcl 19.3mm,cw 13.0mm),Philippines, NHM 1884.31. (A) dorsal; habitus; (B) thoracic sternum and pleon; (C) ventral anterior cephalothorax; (D) carapace, right lateral view." ;
